nodes.text: A Human male Imperial technician worked at a manufacturing plant on Imperial Center in 7 ABY. In one of the plant's warehouses, he was met by undercover agents of the Alien Combine and the New Republic's Rogue Squadron, who were trying to slip him rigged memory cores to be inserted into the planet's central computer system. Having been tipped off, Imperial stormtroopers arrived and began firing at their enemies, and Rogue Leader Wedge Antilles shoved the technician out of his way while escaping.
